text: Yannick Anzuluni (born August 21, 1988) is a Congolese professional basketballer, who currently plays for Rostock Seawolves of the German ProA league. Previously, when he played with Tampereen Pyrintö B team in the Finnish First Division, he was an All-Star, led the league in scoring and steals, and was named Player of the Year. Anzuluni also had a history playing in Canada, with the Quebec Kebs.
